      <h2>
        рџ–ј Smart Compression
      </h2>

      <p>
        Smart compression is&nbsp;a&nbsp;content-aware CDN API method that
        automatically optimizes images for the smallest file size while
        preserving the visual quality.
      </p>

      <p>
        The operation balances out image compression levels and formats.
        It&nbsp;is&nbsp;URL-based and comes included in&nbsp;Adaptive Delivery
        or&nbsp;can be&nbsp;applied separately рџ§ђ
